"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/451802","Department for Education","false","2016-02-23","<p>The Government publishes an unprecedented amount of data; departments publish details of Ministers’ and Permanent Secretaries’ meetings with external organisations, and Special Advisers' meetings with senior media figures. The information requested is not held centrally and there are no plans to extend current arrangements.</p><p> </p>",,"Lord Nash",,"2016-02-23T14:41:26.713Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/451802/answer","Biography information for Lord Nash","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/451802/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/451802/answer",,,,,,,,"60","Education","Education","2016-02-09","Department for Education: Ministerial Policy Advisers","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government whether the Department for Education will publish records of external meetings held by special advisers to its ministers.","false","Biography information for Lord Tyler",,"Lord Tyler","HL6077"
