"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/451050","Prime Minister","false","2016-02-10","<p>Information regarding trade envoys can be found on the gov.uk website.</p>","Witney","Mr David Cameron","25865 ; 25866","2016-02-10T15:57:08.543Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/451050/answer","Biography information for Mr David Cameron","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/451050/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/451050/answer",,,,,,,,"23","Prime Minister","Prime Minister","2016-02-05","Trade Promotion","1","House of Commons","To ask the Prime Minister, which hon. and Right hon. Members have been appointed by him to which countries as a trade envoy.","false","Biography information for David Hanson","Delyn","Mr David Hanson","26060"
